//
// Command-line interface for package management operations.
//
// Usage:
//   quanta [COMMAND] [OPTIONS]
//
// Commands:
//   new         Create a new package
//   init        Initialize a package in existing directory
//   build       Compile the current package
//   run         Build and run the current package
//   test        Run tests
//   bench       Run benchmarks
//   check       Check for errors without building
//   clean       Remove build artifacts
//   doc         Build documentation
//   publish     Publish to registry
//   install     Install a package
//   uninstall   Uninstall a package
//   search      Search for packages
//   update      Update dependencies
//   add         Add a dependency
//   remove      Remove a dependency
//   tree        Display dependency tree
//   fetch       Fetch dependencies
//   login       Login to registry
//   logout      Logout from registry
//
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

